OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMcDonald's workers speak   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fout over sexual abuse      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fclaims                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A toxic culture of sexual assault,     
OL,6, harassment, racism and bullying has    
OL,7, been alleged by more than 100 current  
OL,8, and recent UK staff at outlets of the  
OL,9, fast-food chain McDonald's.            
OL,11,FThe BBC was told that workers, some as 
OL,12,Fyoung as 17, are being groped and      
OL,13,Fharassed almost routinely.             
OL,15,FThe UK equality watchdog said it was   
OL,16,F"concerned" by the BBC's findings and  
OL,17,Fis launching a new email hotline.      
OL,19,FMcDonald's said it had "fallen short"  
OL,20,Fand it "deeply apologised".            
